[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/462] added zip-support to extra
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/453] ``To html``
 and 
``to md``
fdncred 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/460] fixed 1 off table wrapping for help commands
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/458] updated to latest reedline, change config point name, enable output without ansi
, and added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/456] filesize formatting
, and added ability to 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/455] optionally remove table output color
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/451] added default-run so cargo r works
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/449] allowed decimals/floats to be formatted with precision
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/448] enabled 
``cargo build --features=extra``
 to build plugins
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/443] introduced 
``gstat``
, a new command to get the git status
elferherrera created 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/457] dataframe commands name
, and added a 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/442] batch of dataframe commands
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/439] corrected missing shellerror type
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/437] improved labeled error from plugins
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/430] removed unwraps with clippy check
stormasm 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/454] ported over the nth command from nushell
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/446] ported over the prepend command from nushell
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/419] ported over the reject command from nushell
jaeheonji 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/452] ported 
``network/url``
 command
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/440] added random-integer and random-uuid
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/428] added random-dice
onthebridgetonowhere 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/447] ported uniq
, and added 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/429] cal command
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/424] ported str datetime to into datetime
jt 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/441] update clippy to check all features
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/431] improved running main
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/427] added simple commandline args for scripts
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/426] fixed the failure if the prompt breaks
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/425] reset ansi mode more often when showing errors
kubouch 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/engine-q/pull/434] added signature to $scope.commands
